    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Glass, usually borosilicate, with a low coefficient of expansion making it resistant to thermal shock.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
